    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>As you call out words of restoration, up to six creatures of your choice that you can see within range regain hit points equal to 1d4 + your spellcasting ability modifier. This spell has no effect on &amp;Reference[undead]{undead} or constructs.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels. </strong>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the healing increases by 1d4 for each slot level above 3rd.</p>\n</div>",
